# Feature Gates

## Behavior
- Feature gates determine whether vendor edits are:
  - Direct-write
  - Or admin-approved

## Examples
- mapping_edit
- contract_edit
- endpoint_edit
- allowlist_edit

## Invariants
- Feature gates do NOT affect authentication.
- Feature gates do NOT influence vendor identity.
